        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Legal Employment Certification Act of 2010 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to require employers to sign a statement on their income tax returns, under penalties of perjury, that they did not knowingly employ anyone who is not authorized to work in the United States during the taxable year.</p>]]></text>
